                "title": "Poussée"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Compétence élémentaire</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Inflige 1 pt de</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">DGT Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">et accorde une </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">infiltration</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> au personnage.</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Infiltration</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">État</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">DGT subis par le personnage affecté -1 et DGT qu'il inflige +1.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Nombre d'utilisation :</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/02/35653081/2fc519b5fd90708c67fd63a2da75d2d6_8915174194909611743.png",
                "id": "talent86962",
